msgstr "Kredensial API"

msgid "This provider does not require additional credentials."
msgstr "Penyedia ini tidak memerlukan kredensial tambahan."

msgid "Basic Configuration"
msgstr "Konfigurasi Dasar"

msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Nama Tampilan"

msgid "A friendly name to identify this payment provider connection"
msgstr "Nama ramah untuk mengidentifikasi koneksi penyedia pembayaran ini"

msgid "Hosted - Redirect to provider (recommended)"
msgstr "Hosted - Alihkan ke penyedia (direkomendasikan)"

msgid ""
"How customers will complete payment. Hosted mode is more secure and easier "
"to maintain."
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana pelanggan akan menyelesaikan pembayaran. Mode hosted lebih aman "
"dan lebih mudah dipelihara."

msgid ""
"Your credentials will be encrypted using AES-256 encryption before being "
"stored in the database. They are never stored in plain text."
msgstr ""
"Kredensial Anda akan dienkripsi menggunakan enkripsi AES-256 sebelum "
"disimpan di database. Mereka tidak pernah disimpan dalam teks biasa."

msgid "PRODUCTION MODE"
msgstr "MODUS PRODUKSI"

msgid "Using live credentials - real transactions!"
msgstr "Menggunakan kredensial live - transaksi nyata!"

msgid "Verify your"
msgstr "Verifikasi"

msgid "Connection Successful!"
msgstr "Koneksi Berhasil!"

